text: @maddow That depends on whether the northern tier states begin acting up again, and when. If the northern tier states, which have the far higher death rates, get hit by #coronavirus outbreaks again, the death toll might be 250K by 10/1. If not, the death toll likely is 175-190K by 10/1.
